name: Magnificent Fuji-san in the twilight
description: "Magnificent Fuji-san in the twilight" is my first more-than-three-colours work. If we neglect this fact, we get a charming stratovolcano with its history and legends. The volcano is glorious from each side. At the sundown it's snowy top turns to peach-colour, that's why Fuji-san becomes even more beautiful.The price for the work is set based on the rounded height of the volcano <3
